OL,6,FThe public inquiry was set up by the
OL,7,Fprevious government to examine whether
OL,8,Fthe explosion could have been
OL,9,Fprevented by the UK authorities.
OL,11,FThe Real IRA bomb in the Co Tyrone
OL,12,Ftown in August 1998 killed 29 people,
OL,13,Fincluding a woman who was pregnant
OL,14,Fwith twins, in the worst single
OL,15,Fatrocity in the Troubles in Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
