OL,4,Cdetail civil servant risk
OL,6,FBereaved families and their legal
OL,7,Frepresentatives have expressed their
OL,8,Fopposition to any redactions as they
OL,9,Fbelieve it may block getting the
OL,10,Fanswers they want.
OL,12,FMichael Gallagher, who's son Aiden was
OL,13,Fkilled in the 1998 said: "The
OL,14,FSecretary of State is a core
OL,15,Fparticipant as I am, and this is an
OL,16,Findependent public inquiry. That means
OL,17,Findependent of government.
