OL,6,FCounsel for the inquiry Paul Greaney
OL,7,FKC said redactions are slowing the
OL,8,Flegal process down: "The need to
OL,9,Fresolve the issues of redaction has,
OL,10,Fas an objective fact, placed a brake
OL,11,Fon the work of disclosure of the
OL,12,Finquiry."
OL,14,FA barrister for the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fhad argued that unredacted names of
OL,16,Fjunior civil servants put some in
OL,17,Fdanger of attack by dissident
OL,18,Frepublicans.
